{"tid":2057982,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"啲senior 係咪暗地都會嫌棄班細嘅？","createTime":"2020-06-09T21:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T14:58:00.000Z","uid":124938,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0808f2abce8f0bf2d1556e3797218f9dadf00b7d","tid":2057982,"uid":124938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T21:28:45.000Z","msg":"畢咗業成年 喺依間設計公司做咗差唔多一年喇<br />\n但仲係好似乜都唔識咁 乜撚都要senior 幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢係有責任睇住我嘅 但都冇理由乜都要佢執手尾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日佢聽緊其他人brief佢 我聽到啲work係我負責嘅 佢忍唔住爆咗句: 屌啫係我又要做啦<br />\n<br />\n佢嗰吓係口快快唔小心講出嚟 係自然反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻好想喊 好彩坐對面 其他人望唔清我個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得好拖累啲同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好愧疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢平時都冇咩咁 可能個心忍住好耐想屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能冇sense 就係冇sense 啦 想轉行但又諗唔到做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9337340c87b30ec77e8afa59650f5709dca1a70","tid":2057982,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T21:36:47.000Z","msg":"人工問題喳"},{"pid":"dbb6cbcfa92a9d56acd1dbaa6ce3fa91c9708439","tid":2057982,"uid":124938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9337340c87b30ec77e8afa59650f5709dca1a70","tid":2057982,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T21:36:47.000Z","msg":"人工問題喳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T21:40:30.000Z","msg":"依啲時勢都唔會揾到啲好人工嘅工比個冇經驗嘅人啦<img src=\"/